        fn: "OpenTelemetry metrics — unified pipeline with traces",
        desc: "OTel's metrics SDK: same exporter pipeline as traces, OTLP-native, vendor-portable. Pick OTel metrics when you already export traces via OTel and want one collector pipeline.",
